descriptionHtml:
This Is The Cave Of The Damned.

You Can Find It On Your Way To Whiterun From Riverwood.
There Is An Entrance Close To The River.

For Now I Dont Have Plans For It, Maybe It Will Get Something Special In The Future.
You Can Use Version 1.0 As A Player Home If U Want, But There Are No Containers For Your Stuff Or Other Things. 
There Is A Ruined House With Only A Bed, Table And Chair.

How To Install: Put The File In The Skyrim Data Folder.
author: JP0005
